title: About me
feed: I am a highschool senior passionate about maths and coding. I have an extensive background in education and have over a 1000 hours of tutoring grades 1-11. My service is highly personalized, focused on accomodating all the needs of diverse learners.

title: Mission
feed: My mission with every student is to create a plan dedicated towards each student and ensure that the student is learning at a comfortable pace all while still providing them with engaging content
